{
  "stem": "27390.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Used to have even people going around and the, the, the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they used to go around in groups in yards, actors, you know, and perform plays in the yard and it was all in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was all-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was-- in a way, it was marvelous.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "For children, it was very good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A businessman, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Most Jews in Lodz were business people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Not many had trades.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Also, a lot of the trades, you couldn't enter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's another thing, see?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Jews could not enter all trades.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some places were forbidden to them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As I told you before, the guilds, they put a stop on the trades.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Certain trades, if you bribe, you could get a certificate to start a business but in a lot of trades, even if you were prepared to bribe it didn't help.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They wouldn't let in anybody, a Jew in such a-- it was definitely discrimination, no doubt about it, and it wasn't even hidden.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was open.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was taken for granted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, but we didn't-- we-- we-- I was-- we were with Germans all the time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we lived together with them but they were, as I said, ethnic Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were Germans and they were already born in Poland but in the house, they spoke-- like we spoke Yiddish, they spoke German.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And maybe they had some contact with Germany but most of them were Polish and they considered themselves, in a way, Poles, I suppose, up to a point, like we considered ourselves Poles, polish citizens.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They considered themselves Polish citizens.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
